## Harness

This repo enables the shared `harness@claude-harness` plugin via `.claude/settings.json`
(`extraKnownMarketplaces` + `enabledPlugins` + `autoUpdate`). The plugin provides `/plan-change`,
`/create-issue`, `/finish-pr`, the generic `code-reviewer` / `test-runner` subagents, and SessionStart
automation. Pick `autoUpdate` by privilege тАФ see the harness heuristic at
https://github.com/JDSavvy/claude-harness/blob/main/docs/VERSIONING.md
